metadata.name: TURKEY PRAY CHECKS
metadata.description:
Hello Web3!

This open edition is dedicated to assisting individuals impacted by earthquakes in Turkey. 
The funds raised from sales will be directed towards providing humanitarian aid to those affected. 
My aim is to bring peace and comfort to the victims, allowing them to sleep peacefully without any distressing memories.
